data.description:
Call Michelle 570-765-4140 or Gary 570-898-7781 for your private tour today! Beautifully placed house on the hill! Vibrant red siding makes this home stand out from the rest. Enjoy the swimming pool in the summer and the hot tub in the winter. Be close to everything but yet have a great plot of 4.71 acres to enjoy.In the basement you will find an in-law suite that has its own garage space! No need to enter through the main house to enter into the in-law suite. Heated tile floors in the bathroom and kitchen will keep your toes toasty when needed. New carpet in the living room, family room and upstairs. Ahhh. The kitchen is spacious and open! It joins the warmth of the dining room with warm colored trim and also an eat in kitchen. Where cooking and entertaining come together! This home is equipped with the desirable geothermal heating system and superior walls. The driveway is lined with a beautiful split rail fence. A gorgeous view over looking Middleburg! Call us today for your showing. With rising living cost, you can combine your families with this home. 

Explore the potential of this property with a generous $8,000 seller's assistance, offering flexibility for repairs or personalized changes to make it your dream home!
